<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-48-1139 </DOCNO><TEXT>The City of Los Angeles has adopted the Hyperion Energy Recovery Systemas the method for removing sludge from the ocean. In addition to thisobjective, the HERS project will result in the production of approximately10 MW of net energy from the Hyperion Treatment Plant, while meetingstringent air quality standards. The utilization of dewatering, dehydration,combustion, and cogeneration technologies employed as part of the HERSproject represents a unique state-of-the-art sludge management concept.</TEXT></DOC>